Chavez Says Venezuela to Sell Part of Any New Debt in Dollars

-- B y   C o r i n a   R o d r i g u e z   P o n s   a n d   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 
2011-07-09T23:53:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-09/chavez-says-venezuela-to-sell-part-of-any-new-debt-in-dollars.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez  said
part of any new bonds sold by the nation will be denominated in
dollars. Chavez spoke on state television, announcing financial
terms for the expanded debt ceiling approved by the National
Assembly last month.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Corina Pons in Caracas at 
 crpons@bloomberg.net ;
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
 jorozco8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
